    "Herm et al. (2022) discuss the proposed design theory for explainable recommendation systems as part of the design theory implication.",
    "In our research, the empirical data sheds light on the gravity of collecting user preferences on runtime for explainable social media recommender systems.",
    "Therefore, users will not have to engage in multiple interactions with the system, and they will get their intended seamlessly and automatically.",
    "To explain social media recommendations, information related to personal data collection and processing should be included explicitly so that the users feel safe about their online presence and interaction.",
